Usage: specifyIlm [-help] {[-cell <string> [-dir <string>]] | -cellview <string>}

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>          # <Name of cell> (string, optional)
-cellview <string>      # <Specifies the library name, cell name, and view name
                        # in the OpenAccess database format> (string, optional)
-dir <string>           # <Directory path of ilm data> (string, optional)